From 58bbcb626458bed25b9a5a698f43f86584524709 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Aditya Kumar Singh <adisi@qti.qualcomm.com>
Date: Thu, 29 May 2025 15:58:34 +0530
Subject: [PATCH 3/3] wifi: ath12k: process UMAC migration user request

In order to support pirmary UMAC migration, add the base infrastucture
to process the incoming request and to form the list which can be later
used to send command to firmware.

Since in a single shot, multiple peers could be migrated, a linked list
is being maintained which is ready to be migrated. A subsequent change
will accept this list and send command to firmware.

Signed-off-by: Aditya Kumar Singh <quic_adisi@qti.qualcomm.com>
Co-developed-by: Manish Dharanenthiran <mdharane@qti.qualcomm.com>
Signed-off-by: Manish Dharanenthiran <mdharane@qti.qualcomm.com>
